metadata.name: Superlative Structure
metadata.description:
This is the view of Dubai Downtown from Paramount hotel .  The Superlative Skyscrapers of Dubai downtown can be seen from this location. Dubai is beautiful during winter and during night the cities dazzling lights make it special to watch and photograph this amazing city. 

Artist: KIRAN GOVIND 
Captured from Nikon D850 & Nikon 14-24mm f2.8 on Leofoto Tripod 
Item: 1/1
Dimensions:  7966 x 5504  , 240 PPI , 20.2 MB
Date of Capture:  21/02/2022
